{"lemma":"قاصَّةٍ","slug":"قاصَّةٍ","root":"ق.ص.ص","root_slug":"ق-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35691"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to retaliate upon, to make quit"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35691","headword_ar":"قاصّهُ","root":"qS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqaAS~apN","text_ar":"مُقَاصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Mgh, Msb) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaASN","text_ar":"قِصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) [which latter is the more common,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the relation of a slain man, A, Mgh, TA, or one who has been wounded, Mgh, [or mutilated,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retaliated upon him by slaying him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wounding him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Mgh, Msb, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mutilating him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Msb, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to make him quit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even, with him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) See also 8. ―         -b2-  Hence, (A, Mgh,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him quit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even, with himself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"used in a general way. (Mgh.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qAS~ SaAHibahu","text_ar":"قاصّ صَاحِبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, * K,) inf. ns. as above, (Msb,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made his fellow quit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even, with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) in a reckoning, (S, Mgh, K,) or other thing, (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by withholding from him the like of what the latter owed to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made a debt which his fellow owed him to be as a requital of a like debt which he owed his fellow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but Fei adds,] this is taken from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iqotiSaASu AlA^avari","text_ar":"اـِقْتِصَاصُ الاَثَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and hence the former signification, relating to retaliation of slaughter and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2527},{"kind":"text","text":"wounding and mutilation, which, however, is the predominant signification. (Msb.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaASaSotuhu bimaA kaAna liY qabolahu","text_ar":"قَاصَصْتُهُ بِمَا كَانَ لِى قَبْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or, more probably,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qibalahu","text_ar":"قِبَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or perhaps"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I withheld from him the like of what he owed me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ISd says, (TA,) The phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quwS~a zayodN maA Ealayohi","text_ar":"قُوصَّ زَيْدٌ مَا عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been mentioned; and means, in my opinion, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Zeyd was reckoned with for what he owed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"though made trans. without a particle, as implying the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ugorima","text_ar":"اُغْرِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the like. (M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","A","Mgh","S","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}